article.description: — Honor Huff scored 22 points as VMI narrowly defeated Chattanooga 80-75 on Saturday.
article.headline: Huff leads VMI over Chattanooga 80-75
article.story: CHATTANOOGA, Tenn. -- — Honor Huff scored 22 points as VMI narrowly defeated Chattanooga 80-75 on Saturday. Trey Bonham added 20 points and six assists for VMI (16-12, 9-7 Southern Conference). Kamdyn Curfman had 14 points Malachi Smith had 28 points and 10 rebounds for the Mocs (22-7, 12-4). David Jean-Baptiste added 18 points. Darius Banks had five assists. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
